Decompose the problem into a maximum of two focused subproblems to ensure a comprehensive analysis within system constraints. Each helper should address a distinct, necessary dimension of the problem to facilitate a complete resolution.

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}
